## Description {#details}

Cache key for <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/basicaa">BasicAA</a> results.

It only includes the pointer and size from <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/memorylocation">MemoryLocation</a>, as <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/basicaa">BasicAA</a> is AATags independent. Additionally, it includes the value of MayBeCrossIteration, which may affect <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/basicaa">BasicAA</a> results.

Definition at line 200 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/analysis/aliasanalysis-h">AliasAnalysis.h</a>.
